casebody.data:
James GILLER, petitioner,
v.
ORACLE USA, INC. No. 13-355. Supreme Court of the United States Nov. 4, 2013. Case below, 512 Fed.Appx. 71 . Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied. Justice ALITO took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
